Uses of Package
FESI.gui

Packages that use FESI.gui
FESI.awtgui Implements the gui interfaces for the AWT. 
FESI.gui Defines the interface of the gui functions, so that they can be implemented with AWT and Swing. 
FESI.Interpreter Contains the interpreter itself (the xxxVisitor classes), then driver routines (Evaluator), the interactive interpreter (Interpret) and may utility classes. 
FESI.swinggui Contains the implementation of the gui functions defined in the interfaces of the package gui.
